64 process.
65 (8) The use or consumption of electricity by an
66 incorporated municipality, a board, or corporation organized
67 under the authority of any incorporated municipality in
68 furnishing or providing street lighting or traffic-control
69 systems; the use or consumption of telephone services by an
70 incorporated municipality in providing fire alarm systems; and
