77 (10) The furnishing of utility services through the use
78 of a prepaid telephone calling card.
79 (11)a. The furnishing of natural gas or liquefied
80 petroleum gas for use or consumption as fuel or energy in the
81 construction of any public highway, road, or bridge.
82 b. This exclusion may only be claimed by a contractor
83 licensed by the State Licensing Board for General Contractors,
84 or a subcontractor working under the same contract, for use
